'''衛星DNA'''由串联排列、不断重复的[[非編碼DNA|非編碼DNA]]组成，它是[[着絲粒|着絲粒]]的主要组成部分，也是[[異染色質|異染色質]]的主要结构部分<ref>{{cite book|author=Knight, Julian C.|title=Human Genetic Diversity: Functional Consequences for Health and Disease|publisher=Oxford University Press|year=2009|isbn=978-0-19-922769-3|page=167|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=NSLeurRJWsIC&pg=PA167|access-date=2015-12-05|archive-date=2021-04-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210427060923/https://books.google.com/books?id=NSLeurRJWsIC&pg=PA167|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

